          <div class="title-line "></div>
          </span>
          <p>Many hiring managers create an ad regarding some vacancy on job boards or portals online and create online test forms on some other channels in which filtering out the best candidate for the job is a very tiring process. Hiring managers always experience time consuming process in selecting a best candidate through the screening process.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
