          <li class="list-group-item">A job posting portal where hiring manager can post a job related information in detailed manner and can also define hiring flows for his team. The step-by-step wizard will help hiring manager to create comprehensive job-related details and gather candidate profile data.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-3">
        <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
          <li class="list-group-item font-weight-bold">ONLINE TEST CREATION</li>
          <li class="list-group-item">A solid online test creation experience where hiring manager can design an online test for the candidate for screening purposes. Test includes manual and automatic scoring by system.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-3">
        <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
          <li class="list-group-item font-weight-bold">FILTERING BEST CANDIDATE</li>
          <li class="list-group-item">A detailed ken-ben design of hiring flow experience where the intelligent system filters out best suitable candidate based on automatic scoring by system & manual scoring by reviewers in no time which saves lots of hours of manual screening process.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-3">
        <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
          <li class="list-group-item font-weight-bold">CONDUCT ONLINE VIDEO INTERVIEWS</li>
          <li class="list-group-item">Allowing hiring managers to invite filtered out candidates along with other team members for online video interviews from the same portal.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
